var e=JSON.parse(`[{"id":"L2_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"당연히 아시겠지만, 대정화전쟁 때 많은 사람들이 안타까운 비극을 겪었습니다.","JPN":"みんな知っていると思いますが、大浄化戦争で多くの人々が不運な悲劇を経験しました。","ENG":"As you may already know, many suffered unfortunate tragedies during the Great Purification War.","TWN":"如你所知，在大淨化戰爭期間，許多人遭遇了無可挽回的悲劇。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L3_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그땐 우리 모두가 피해자였고, 어린 아이들은 누군가의 도움 없인 살아남을 수 없었죠.","JPN":"あの時には私たちみんなが被害者で、幼い子どもたちは誰かの助けなしでは生き残れなかったのです。","ENG":"At that time, we were all victims. Young children could not survive unless someone assisted them.","TWN":"那時我們全都是受害者，年幼的孩子若沒有他人幫助，根本無法活下來。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L4_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이곳에서 생활하는 많은 자매들이 그 시절에 거둬들인 연고 없는 아이들입니다.","JPN":"ここで生活している多くの姉妹たちはあの頃に引き取った、家族なき子です。","ENG":"Many of the sisters who have settled here were the children from that era.","TWN":"在這裡生活的許多修女，都是當年收留的孤兒。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"프라이머 자매님도 그 중 한 명이죠.","JPN":"プライマー姉妹もその中の1人です。","ENG":"Sister Primer was also one of them.","TWN":"布萊伊莫修女也是其中之一。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"자매님은 어렸을 때부터 불의를 좌시하지 않는 올곧은 심성을 가지고 있었습니다.","JPN":"姉妹は小さい頃から不義から目を背けない、真っすぐな心を持っていました。","ENG":"From a young age, Sister Primer had a strong sense of justice.","TWN":"她從小就很正直，無法對不公不義視而不見。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L8_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"열 살 땐 몰래 외출을 나간 아이를 데려오다 폭력배들과 싸웠고…","JPN":"10歳の時にはこっそり家出した子を連れて帰る途中、ならず者とケンカし……","ENG":"At the age of ten, she fought against gangsters while bringing back the children who snuck out...","TWN":"十歲時，她曾為了帶回私自外出的孩子，與不良分子動手……"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"성인식을 치른 해엔 수도원을 점거하려던 극성테러 조직을 쫓아내기도 했어요.","JPN":"成人式の後には修道院を占拠しようとした過激テロ組織を追い払ったこともありました。","ENG":"And on the year of her coming of age ceremony, she even chased out a terrorist organization that was trying to take over the monastery.","TWN":"成年禮那年，甚至驅逐企圖佔領修道院的激進恐怖組織。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"물론 기특하고 자랑스럽지요. 프라이머 자매님을 보면 어떤 불의 앞에서도 고개를 돌리지 않을 거란 확신이 느껴졌습니다.","JPN":"もちろん健気で自慢に思います。プライマー姉妹を見ていると、どんな不義の前でも目を背けないという確信を感じました。","ENG":"Of course, I am proud of her. Looking at Sister Primer, I am confident that she would not turn her back on any injustice.","TWN":"當然，這樣的表現令人驕傲。每當看著布萊伊莫修女，我都覺得她絕不會在任何不義之事前低頭。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그렇기 때문에 난 늘 걱정이 앞섰어요. 자신이 감당하지 못할 무모한 정의는 결국 자신을 망가뜨리게 될 테니 말이죠.","JPN":"だからこそ私はいつも心配だったのです。手に負えない無謀な正義は、結局自分自身を壊すことになるはずですから。","ENG":"That is also why I am concerned about her. One day, she will destroy herself by attempting to handle justice she is incapable of handling.","TWN":"但也正因如此，我總是先替她感到擔心。因為無法承擔的魯莽正義，最終只會毀了自己。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그래서 성황청의 신부들이 찾아왔을 때, 저는 자매님이 시험을 치르게 했습니다.","JPN":"それで聖皇庁の神父たちが訪ねて来た時、私は姉妹に試験を受けさせました。","ENG":"So when the priests of the Holy Curia came to visit, I made Sister Primer take the test.","TWN":"所以當聖皇廳的神父來訪時，我讓她接受測試。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"정식 퇴마사가 되어 그에 걸맞은 힘을 기른다면, 그 정의로운 마음도 한층 견고해질 테니까요.","JPN":"正式のエクソシストになり、それ相応の力を養えば、正義に溢れる心も一段と強くなるはずでしょうから。","ENG":"If she were to become an official exorcist and gain the necessary strength, her righteousness would grow even stronger.","TWN":"若能成為正式的驅魔師、獲得相應的力量，那份正義之心也會更加堅定。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L14_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"조사를 했다면 아시겠지만, 퇴마사가 되는 것이 결코 쉬운 길은 아닙니다. 무엇보다 성황청의 인정을 받기 위한 세 가지 시험에서 통과해야 하죠.","JPN":"調べたらわかると思いますが、エクソシストになるのは決して簡単なことではありません。何より聖皇庁から認められるために、三つの試験で合格する必要があります。","ENG":"If you have done your research, you will understand that becoming an exorcist is not an easy task. Above all, one must pass three tests before being recognized by the Holy Curia.","TWN":"如果你調查過便會知道，成為驅魔師絕不是件容易的事，必須通過聖皇廳認可的三項測驗才行。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L15_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"프라이머 자매님은 비록 마지막 시험에서 떨어지긴 했지만, 신부님들께선 논의 끝에 자매님을 데려가기로 결정했습니다.","JPN":"プライマー姉妹は最後の試験で脱落してしまいましたが、神父たちは議論の末、姉妹を連れて行くことにしました。","ENG":"Sister Primer may have failed her final exam, but after much deliberation, the priests decided to accept her.","TWN":"雖然布萊伊莫修女在最後一項測驗失敗了，神父經過討論後仍決定帶走她。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L16_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아마도 앞선 두 가지 시험에서 충분히 퇴마사의 자질을 인정받았기 때문이겠지요.","JPN":"おそらくその前に二つの試験で、十分とエクソシストの資質を認めてもらったのでしょう。","ENG":"Perhaps it is because the previous two tests sufficiently demonstrated her qualifications to become an exorcist.","TWN":"大概是因為在前兩項測驗中，她已經充分證明了自己的資質吧。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"떨어진 마지막 시험이 뭐였냐고요?","JPN":"脱落した最後の試験は何だったのか気になりますか？","ENG":"What was the last test she failed, you ask?","TWN":"你問最後落敗的測驗是什麼啊？"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L18_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ABBESS_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"후후, 우리 용감한 자매님도 무서워하는 게 하나쯤은 있거든요.","JPN":"ふふ、勇敢な姉妹にも怖いものが1つくらいあるのです。","ENG":"Haha, even the courageous Sister Primer is afraid of something.","TWN":"呵呵，我們那位勇敢的修女也有害怕的東西呢。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_01","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L21_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"어서오세요, 손님…","JPN":"いらっしゃいませ、お客様……","ENG":"Welcome to Gremory's Bar–","TWN":"歡迎光臨，客人……"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"으갸아아악!!!","JPN":"ふんぎゃあああぁっ！！！","ENG":"WHOAA!!","TWN":"呀啊啊啊！！！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_NOISE_FIGHT"},{"id":"L25_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"니콜이 그런 이상한 비명을 지르다니. 별일이구나.","JPN":"ニコルがそのような変な悲鳴をあげるとは。珍しいな。","ENG":"I didn't know Nicole could scream like that. How strange.","TWN":"妮可居然會發出那種奇怪的尖叫聲，還真少見。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"모모! 저기…가게에… 고양이가 들어왔어요!","JPN":"モモ！　あそこ……店に……猫が入ってきました！","ENG":"Momo! Th-there's... a c-cat... in the bar!","TWN":"莫莫！那個……店裡……有、有貓跑進來了！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"고양이?","JPN":"猫？","ENG":"A cat?","TWN":"貓？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L28_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"어머, 실례했어요. 아무래도 제 동료가 바텐더 아가씨를 겁준 모양이네요.","JPN":"あら、失礼。どうやら私の仲間がバーテンダーのお嬢さんを怖がらせてしまったようね。","ENG":"Oh, excuse me. It seems my little colleague scared your bartender.","TWN":"啊，不好意思。看來是我的同伴嚇到這位調酒師小姐了。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L29_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"냥?","JPN":"ニャ？","ENG":"Meow?","TWN":"喵？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L30_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"고양이를 데리고 다니는 수상한 손님이로구나. 정체를 밝히거라.","JPN":"猫を連れている怪しいお客さんだな。正体を明かせ。","ENG":"What a suspicious customer, bringing a cat to a bar. Reveal yourself!","TWN":"原來是帶著貓到處走的可疑客人啊？麻煩自我介紹一下。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L31_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"근처에서 카페를 운영하고 있는 직원이예요. 새 가게가 들어왔다길래, 이웃 분들에게 인사차 들렀답니다.","JPN":"この辺りのカフェで働いている職員だわ。新しい店ができたって聞いたから、ご近所さんに挨拶をしようと思って。","ENG":"I work at a nearby cafe. I came to say hello after hearing about the new bar that had opened.","TWN":"我是附近咖啡廳的員工。聽說這裡新開了一家店，就過來跟鄰居打聲招呼。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L33_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"혹시 그쪽이 점장님?","JPN":"もしかして、あなたが店長？","ENG":"Are you the manager?","TWN":"請問你是店長嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L34_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"점장 같은 하찮은 일은 이 몸의 하수인인 그레모리가 맡고 있지. 지금은 외출 중이니라.","JPN":"店長のようなくだらない仕事は吾輩の下僕、グレモリーが受け持っている。今は外出中だ。","ENG":"Tedious tasks like managing are done by my subject, Gremory. But she's out right now.","TWN":"店長那種瑣碎的工作，是交給我的手下葛茉莉負責的。她現在不在。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L35_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"점장이 하수인이면, 꼬마아가씨는 어떤 일을 하는데?","JPN":"店長が下僕なら、お嬢ちゃんはどんな仕事をしているの？","ENG":"If the manager is your subject, what do you do, little lady?","TWN":"如果店長是手下，那這位小妹妹是負責什麼的呢？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L36_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이 몸은 달콤한 주스를 만들 수 있노라.","JPN":"吾輩は甘いジュースを作れるのだ。","ENG":"I can make sweet juice.","TWN":"我負責製作香甜的果汁。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L37_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하긴. 이렇게 귀여우면 아무것도 안 해도 손님이 몰려들겠는걸?","JPN":"確かに。これだけ可愛いと、何もしなくてもお客さんが押し寄せてきそうね。","ENG":"I guess, being as cute as you are, you would still attract a large number of customers even if you did nothing.","TWN":"也對。你這麼可愛，就算什麼都不做，客人也會蜂擁而至吧？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L41_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"무엄햐구냐, 갸미 이 모메 볼을 자뱌 당기댜니.","JPN":"けしきゃらん、わがひゃいのほおをひっぴゃるとは。","ENG":"Hao dayr you. Hao dayr you pin'h ma sheeks la'ch dat?","TWN":"放肆！竟敢捏我的臉！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L42_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아 참, 이건 저희 카페에서 만든 디저트예요. 페이스트리에 치즈와 블루베리를 얹은 특제 카나페랍니다.","JPN":"あ、そうだわ。これはうちのカフェで作ったデザート。ペイストリーにチーズとブルーベリーを乗せた特製カナッペよ。","ENG":"Oh, right. This is a dessert we make at our cafe. It's a special canapé topped with cheese and blueberries.","TWN":"對了，這是我們咖啡廳製作的甜點。是在派皮上加了起司與藍莓的特製開胃小點。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L44_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"오오, 블루베리! 디저트! 하수인의 재목으로 손색이 없도다!","JPN":"おお、ブルーベリー！　デザート！　下僕に相応しい人材だな！","ENG":"Ooh! Blueberries! Dessert! You are worthy of being my subject as well!","TWN":"哦哦，藍莓！甜點！你很有當手下的天分！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS2"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L45_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그나저나 실망이구나, 니콜. 이 몸의 하수인이 이런 작고 귀여운 생물을 두려워하다니.","JPN":"それにしてもがっかりだぞ、ニコル。吾輩の下僕たるものが、このような小さくて可愛い生物を怖がるとは。","ENG":"Anyway, I'm disappointed in you, Nicole. How can a subject of mine be scared of such a small and cute creature?","TWN":"話說回來，妮可你真讓我失望啊。身為我的手下，竟然會怕這種小巧可愛的生物。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L46_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그르릉…","JPN":"ガルルン……","ENG":"Purrr...","TWN":"咕嗚……"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}},"sfx":"FX_COMBAT_CAT_START"},{"id":"L48_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그, 그래도 무서운 걸 어떡해요!","JPN":"で、でも怖いんです！","ENG":"I-I can't help that I'm afraid of cats!","TWN":"可、可是我就是會怕嘛！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L50_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"저 빳빳한 귀와 노려보는 눈동자 좀 보세요!","JPN":"あのピンと立ってる耳と、睨んでくる瞳を見てくださいよ！","ENG":"Just look at those stiff ears and glaring eyes!","TWN":"你看看那直挺挺的耳朵，還有盯著人的眼神！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L2_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"분명 방심하는 순간 소리 없이 달려들어서 얼굴을 할퀼 거라고요!","JPN":"きっと油断した途端に音もなく飛びかかって顔を引っ掻くはずです！","ENG":"The moment I put my guard down, he'll rush at me and scratch my face!","TWN":"牠肯定會趁我不注意的時候，悄悄撲上來抓我的臉！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L5_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"냐앙…","JPN":"ニャーン……","ENG":"Meow...","TWN":"喵……"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}},"sfx":"FX_COMBAT_CAT_START"},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"꼬마아가씨는 간식 가지고 잠깐 밖에서 고양이랑 놀고 있을래? 바텐더 양이 계속 구석에 웅크리고 있으면 인사를 못 할 것 같거든.","JPN":"お嬢ちゃんはおやつを持って外で猫とちょっと遊んでいてくれる？　バーテンダーさんがずっと隅っこでうずくまっていると挨拶ができそうにないから。","ENG":"Would you like to take the treats and play with the cat outside, little lady? I doubt I'll be able to say hello if your bartender remains crouched in the corner.","TWN":"小妹妹要不要拿著點心，到外面陪貓玩一下呢？調酒師小姐一直躲在角落，我沒辦法好好和她講話。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"걱정 말거라! 야옹이는 이 몸이 잘 돌보고 있으마!","JPN":"心配するでない！　猫ちゃんは吾輩がお世話をするとしよう！","ENG":"Don't you worry! I shall take good care of the kitty!","TWN":"別擔心！貓咪就交給我照顧吧！"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"MOMO_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"CAT_STREGA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이제 괜찮아. 고양이는 이제 없으니까.","JPN":"大丈夫よ。猫はもういないから。","ENG":"It's all right now. The cat's gone.","TWN":"現在沒事了，貓已經不在店裡了。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이웃분에게 첫인상부터 꼴사나운 모습을 보였네요.","JPN":"ご近所さんに初対面からみっともない姿を見せちゃいましたね。","ENG":"Well, this is an embarrassing first impression to make on our neighbor.","TWN":"我從第一印象開始，就在鄰居面前出糗了呢。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아니야. 사전에 정보도 없이 고양이를 데려온 내 잘못이지.","JPN":"ううん。何の断りも入れずに猫を連れてきた私が悪かったの。","ENG":"No. It's my fault that I brought my cat without any warning.","TWN":"不，是我不好，沒事先說一聲就帶貓過來。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"}}}},{"id":"L14_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"여기 귀여운 꼬마가 있다고 해서, 동물을 데려오면 좋아할 것 같았거든.","JPN":"ここに可愛いお嬢ちゃんがいると聞いて、動物を連れてきたら喜ぶと思ってね。","ENG":"I just heard there was a cute girl here, and I figured she'd be interested in seeing a cute pet.","TWN":"我聽說這裡有個可愛的小孩，才會想說帶動物來，她應該會喜歡。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L15_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"소문대로 정말 깜찍하네. 뿔 악세서리도 잘 어울리고 말이야.","JPN":"噂どおり、本当に可愛いね。角のアクセサリーもよく似合っているし。","ENG":"Guess the rumors were true. She's adorable. Even the horn accessory fits her well.","TWN":"她果然跟傳聞一樣可愛呢，角形裝飾也很適合她。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L16_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아하하… 그럼요. 단골 손님들도 모모를 보려고 자주 찾으세요.","JPN":"あはは……そうなんです。常連さんもみんなモモに会うためによく来ますよ。","ENG":"Ah hah hah... Yeah. A lot of our regulars come to see Momo too.","TWN":"啊哈哈……是啊，常客們也為了看莫莫常常過來。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L18_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"흐음, 바텐더 양은 좋은 향수를 쓰는 모양이네.","JPN":"ふーん、バーテンダーさんはとてもいい香水を使っているようね。","ENG":"Hmm, I see that you have a good taste for perfumes.","TWN":"嗯，調酒師小姐似乎用了不錯的香水。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L20_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"정말요? 아침에 너무 정신 없이 뿌렸나?","JPN":"本当ですか？　朝に慌ててつけすぎたのかな？","ENG":"Really? Did I put on too much this morning?","TWN":"真的嗎？我早上噴太多了嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L21_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"괜찮아. 직업 특성상 내 코가 예민한 거니까.","JPN":"大丈夫よ。職業柄、私の鼻が敏感なだけだから。","ENG":"It's okay. I just have a good sense of smell because of my job.","TWN":"不會，我只是因為工作的關係，嗅覺比較敏銳。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L22_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"향이 괜찮길래 나도 같은 걸로 하나 장만할까 싶어서.","JPN":"いい香りで、私も同じものを買おうかって思ったの。","ENG":"I found it smells so good that I'm considering buying one for myself.","TWN":"味道很不錯，我都想買一瓶來用了。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L23_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"글쎄요. 저희 점장님이 선물해주신 거라서요. 점장님께 물어봐서 다음번에 찾아오시면 알려드릴게요.","JPN":"さあ。店長がプレゼントしてくれたものなんですよ。店長に聞いてみて、今度来たら教えますね。","ENG":"Well. Our manager gave it to me. I'll ask her what it is and let you know the next time you come over.","TWN":"這是我們店長送的禮物。我去問問店長，等你下次來的時候再告訴你。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그래주면 나야 고맙지. 나도 칵테일 좋아하니까. 다음번에 또 찾아올게.","JPN":"そうしてくれると嬉しいわ。私もカクテルが好きだから、今度また来るね。","ENG":"I'd be grateful for that. I do like cocktails, so I'll make sure to come by again.","TWN":"那就太好了。雞尾酒我也很喜歡，下次還會再來的。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L25_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"좋아요. 그럼 오늘은 서비스로 한 잔 드릴게요. 특별히 선호하시는 술 있으세요?","JPN":"いいですよ。じゃあ、今日は特別にサービスで。好きなお酒はあるんですか？","ENG":"Sounds good. Then how about one on the house? Is there a particular spirit you prefer?","TWN":"好啊，那我今天就請你喝一杯。你有特別偏好什麼酒嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"마르가리타. 버진으로 부탁해. 곧 가게에 돌아가봐야 하거든.","JPN":"マルガリータ。バージンでお願いね。もうすぐ店に戻らないといけないから。","ENG":"A margarita, please. And make it virgin at that. I have to go back to my shop right after.","TWN":"我想要無酒精的瑪格麗特，等等還得回去顧店。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_03","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EVELYN_STREGA_EVERY_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L29_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"내가 자릴 비운 동안 근처 가게 직원분이 찾아오셨다고?","JPN":"アタシが留守していた間に、近所の店の職員が来た？","ENG":"An employee from a nearby cafe came to visit while I was away?","TWN":"聽說我不在的時候，有附近店家的員工來過？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L30_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"네, 디저트 카페에서 일한다고 하시던데. 스타일이나 말투가 무척 세련된 분이었어요.","JPN":"はい、デザートカフェで働いてるって言ってました。スタイルとか口調がとてもオシャレな方でしたよ。","ENG":"Yes. She said she works at a dessert cafe. Her style and manner were very sophisticated.","TWN":"對，她說在甜點咖啡廳工作，打扮和談吐都很有品味。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L31_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"카페 스트레가네. 맞지?","JPN":"カフェストレガね。そうでしょう？","ENG":"Cafe Strega, right?","TWN":"是史特雷加咖啡廳對吧？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L35_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그걸 어떻게 아셨어요?","JPN":"なんで知ってるんですか？","ENG":"How did you know?","TWN":"您怎麼知道？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_HATE"}}}},{"id":"L36_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"간단해. 그라운드 원에서 고양이가 명물인 디저트 카페는 한 곳 밖에 없으니까.","JPN":"簡単よ。グラウンド・ワンで猫が名物のデザートカフェは一か所しかないわ。","ENG":"Simple. There's only one dessert cafe in Ground One where a cat is its mascot.","TWN":"很簡單啊。在G1以貓聞名的甜點咖啡廳只有那一家。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_HATE"}}}},{"id":"L37_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"선물로 받은 카나페가 무척 맛있더라고요. 와인이랑도 잘 어울리고.","JPN":"プレゼントに貰ったカナッペがとても美味しかったんです。ワインともよく合うし。","ENG":"The canapé she gave us was delicious! It paired well with wine too.","TWN":"她送的開胃小點很好吃，也很適合配紅酒。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L38_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"종종 들러서 디저트 좀 사올게요. 그레모리 씨도 과자 좋아하시죠?","JPN":"たまに寄ってデザートを買ってきますね。グレモリーさんもお菓子好きなんでしょう？","ENG":"I'll stop by there every now and then and buy us desserts. Do you like cookies, Gremory?","TWN":"我之後也會常去買些甜點回來。葛茉莉小姐也喜歡餅乾吧？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"}}}},{"id":"L39_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그럼. 난 술이랑 어울리는 건 뭐든 괜찮아.","JPN":"もちろん。アタシはお酒と合うなら何でもいいわ。","ENG":"Of course. I like anything that pairs well with alcohol.","TWN":"當然，只要是能配酒的我都喜歡。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"}}}},{"id":"L40_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그나저나 우리 꼬마 임금님은 벌써 잠든 건가?","JPN":"それより、王様はもうお休み？","ENG":"Anyway, has our little majesty already gone to bed?","TWN":"話說回來，我們的小小國王已經睡了嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"}}}},{"id":"L41_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"네, 고양이랑 엄청 잘 어울려 놀더니 지쳐서 잠들더라고요.","JPN":"はい、猫とめちゃくちゃ遊んで疲れて寝ちゃったんです。","ENG":"Yes. She was exhausted from playing with the cat all day.","TWN":"對。她剛剛跟貓玩得很開心，結果累到睡著了。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_LAUGH"}}}},{"id":"L42_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"…겁이 많은 저랑은 다르게 말이죠, 하하.","JPN":"……怖がり屋の私とは違って、はは。","ENG":"...Unlike me, who's afraid of cats... Hah hah.","TWN":"……跟膽小的我完全不一樣呢，哈哈。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"}}}},{"id":"L43_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"의외네. 무시무시한 범죄조직 앞에서도 당당하던 니콜 양이 고양이를 무서워하다니.","JPN":"意外ね。恐ろしい犯罪組織の前でも堂々としていたニコルちゃんが猫を怖がるなんて。","ENG":"That's odd. Nicole Primer, who is fearless in the face of criminal organizations, is afraid of cats?","TWN":"真意外。面對兇狠的犯罪組織都能泰然自若的妮可小姐，居然會怕貓。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"}}}},{"id":"L44_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하하, 그게… 어렸을 때 그럴 만한 일이 좀 있었거든요.","JPN":"はは、それが……小さい頃にちょっとあったんですよ。","ENG":"Hah hah, well... Something happened when I was little.","TWN":"哈哈，那個……小時候發生過一些事。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"}}}},{"id":"L46_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그런데 그 손님. 무슨 술을 주문했었어?","JPN":"ところで、あのお客さん。どんなお酒を注文したの？","ENG":"By the way. That customer. What did she order?","TWN":"對了，那位客人點了什麼酒？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L47_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"주문한 술이요? 그게… 버진 마가리타였어요.","JPN":"注文したお酒ですか？　それが……バージンマルガリータだったんです。","ENG":"Her order? Um... It was a virgin margarita.","TWN":"她點的酒嗎？嗯……是無酒精的瑪格麗特。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"GREMORY_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"BARTENDER_BAR_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L50_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"저 아이도 데려가겠습니다.","JPN":"あの子も連れて行きます。","ENG":"We shall take that child as well.","TWN":"我也要帶走那個孩子。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_PHONE"},{"id":"L1_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하지만 신부님, 그녀는 세번째 시험을 통과하지 못했습니다.","JPN":"ですが神父、彼女は3度目の試験に合格できませんでした。","ENG":"But sir, she did not pass the third test.","TWN":"但是神父，她並沒有通過第三項測驗。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L2_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"상관없습니다. 이미 첫번째 시험에서 결정됐으니까요.","JPN":"構いません。すで最初の試験で決められたのですから。","ENG":"No matter. It was decided after her first test.","TWN":"無妨，早在第一項測驗時就已經決定結果了。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L3_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"제가 감히 신부님의 뜻을 의심하는 건 아니지만, 탈락자를 후보로 선별하는 전례는 없는 걸로 압니다.","JPN":"私が神父の意志を疑っているわけではないですが、脱落した者を候補として選ぶ前例はなかったはずです。","ENG":"I dare not doubt your intentions, but there has been no precedent for selecting failed candidates.","TWN":"我並非質疑神父的判斷，只是將淘汰者列為候補，實在前所未聞。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L4_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"…이러한 판단은 심의회의 교리에 어긋나지 않습니까?","JPN":"……このような判断は審議会の教理に反するのでは？","ENG":"...Do these decisions not contradict the Investigation Council's doctrine?","TWN":"……這樣的決定，難道沒有違背議會的教義嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L5_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"저희는 재능만이 가능성의 전부라고 생각하지 않기 때문입니다.","JPN":"私たちは才能だけが可能性のすべてだとは思いません。","ENG":"We do not think that talent is all of one's potential.","TWN":"因為我們不認為才能就是一切。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"신부님도 보셨잖습니까? 고작 고양이 한 마리 때문에 시험을 포기하는 모습을요.","JPN":"神父も見ていたのではありませんか。たかが猫1匹で試験を諦める姿を。","ENG":"But you saw it too, did you not? She gave up the test for a cat.","TWN":"神父您也看到了吧？她竟然因為一隻貓就放棄測驗。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"첫번째 시험이 총을 쏘는 재능을 확인하는 시험이라면, 세번째 시험은 선택의 갈등 앞에서 망설이지 않는 결단력을 확인하는 것입니다.","JPN":"最初の試験が銃を撃つ才能を確認する試験なら、三度目の試験は選択の岐路で迷わない決断力を確認するものです。","ENG":"If the first test was seeing one's talent in shooting a gun, the third was to see one's unwavering determination in the face of conflict.","TWN":"若說第一項測驗是檢驗射擊才能，那麼第三項測驗，就是要確認在抉擇的矛盾前毫不猶豫的決心。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L8_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그 아이의 여린 마음이 언젠가 발목을 잡게 될까 걱정이군요.","JPN":"あの子の弱い心がいつか足手まといになるのではと心配です。","ENG":"I worry that her tender heart might get in her way one day.","TWN":"我擔心她過於軟弱的心，終有一天會成為絆腳石。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그 말씀에는 저도 동의합니다.","JPN":"その話には私も同感です。","ENG":"I concur.","TWN":"這點我也同意。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"니콜 자매가 보여준 행동은 퇴마사의 자격으로선 실격이죠.","JPN":"ニコル姉妹が見せてくれた行動は、エクソシストの資格としては失格です。","ENG":"The actions of Sister Nicole exempt her from becoming an exorcist.","TWN":"妮可修女的表現，確實不符合驅魔師的資格。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하지만 심의회가 제시하는 세 가지 시험은, 세 가지의 근거를 찾는 의례이기도 합니다.","JPN":"ですが、審議会が提示する3つの試験は3つの根拠を探す儀礼でもあります。","ENG":"However, the three tests presented by the Council are also a rite of finding three rationales.","TWN":"然而，議會設下的三道測驗，也可說是尋找三個依據的儀式。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그리고 니콜 자매는 하나의 <color=#ffd34c>근거</color>를 충족했습니다.","JPN":"そしてニコル姉妹は一つの<color=#ffd34c>根拠</color>を十分満たしています。","ENG":"And Sister Nicole has met one of those <color=#ffd34c>rationales</color>.","TWN":"而妮可修女已經滿足了其中一項<color=#ffd34c>依據</color>。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L14_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"HEAD_NPC_PARISH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"…이것은?","JPN":"……これは？","ENG":"...What is this?","TWN":"……這是指？"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L15_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그녀가 첫번째 시험에 앞서 선택한 총입니다.","JPN":"彼女が最初の試験前に選択した銃です。","ENG":"This is the gun she chose before her first test.","TWN":"這是她在第一項測驗前選擇的槍。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L16_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"평범한 사람이라면 눈길조차 주지 않겠지만, 그녀는 자연스럽게 손을 뻗었죠.","JPN":"普通の人間なら目も向けないはずですが、彼女は自然と手を伸ばしたのです。","ENG":"A normal person would have never given it a glance, but she naturally reached for it.","TWN":"換作一般人，恐怕連看都不會多看一眼，但她卻毫不猶豫伸出手。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이것이 제가 그녀를 후보로 선별한 근거입니다.","JPN":"これが私が彼女を候補として選んだ根拠です。","ENG":"That is why I selected her as a candidate.","TWN":"這正是我將她列為候補的依據。"},"stage":{"bg":"GREMORY_BAR","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L19_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"자매님들에게 인사는 다 마쳤습니까?","JPN":"姉妹方との挨拶は済みましたか？","ENG":"Have you said goodbye to all the other sisters?","TWN":"你和各個修女都打過招呼了嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L21_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_NPC_YOUNG_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"네! 신부님!","JPN":"はい！　神父様！","ENG":"Yes, sir!","TWN":"是！神父！"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L22_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그렇다면 이것을 받도록 하십시오. 자매님의 먼 여정길에 벗이 되어줄 테니.","JPN":"なら、これを受け取ってください。姉妹の長い旅の友になってくれるでしょう。","ENG":"Then please, take this. It will be your companion throughout your journey.","TWN":"那請你收下這個，它會在修女漫長的旅途上陪伴你。"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L23_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_NPC_YOUNG_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"와아, 감사합니다! 잘 간직하겠습니다!","JPN":"わあ、ありがとうございます！　大事にしますね！","ENG":"Wow, thank you! I'll keep it well!","TWN":"哇啊，謝謝您！我一定會好好珍惜的！"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_NOISE_RUSTLE_04"},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_NPC_YOUNG_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그런데, 이것의 이름은 무엇인가요?","JPN":"ところで、これの名前はなんですか？","ENG":"But, does it have a name?","TWN":"可是，請問它的名字是什麼呢？"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L25_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"호오, 스승 될 사람을 앞에 두고 물건의 이름을 먼저 물어본 건 자매님이 처음이군요.","JPN":"ほお、師匠になる人の前で物の名前を先に聞いてきたのは姉妹が初めてですね。","ENG":"Ho-oh, you are the first to ask the name of an object before your master-to-be.","TWN":"哦？在未來的導師面前先詢問物品名字的，修女你還是第一個呢。"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_NPC_YOUNG_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아… 으앗?! 죄, 죄송합니다!","JPN":"あ……わあっ！？　す、すみません！","ENG":"Oh... Huh?! I-I'm sorry!","TWN":"啊……咦？！對、對不起！"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그것의 이름은 아가테입니다. 앞으로의 시련을 헤쳐나가게 될 자매님의 벗이죠.","JPN":"それの名前はアガーテ。これから一緒に試練をくぐり抜ける姉妹の友なのです。","ENG":"It is called Agathe. It will be your friend as you face the trials ahead.","TWN":"它叫艾卡特，也是今後將陪伴修女度過試煉的夥伴。"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L28_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_NPC_YOUNG_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아가테… 라고 하는군요. 어쩐지 친숙한 이름이에요!","JPN":"アガーテ……なんですね。なんだか親しみのある名前です！","ENG":"Agathe... It sounds really familiar to me!","TWN":"原來叫艾卡特……啊。總覺得這個名字很熟悉呢！"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L29_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"PRIEST_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"저희에게 있어서도, 자매님에게 있어서도, 소중한 보물입니다. 그러니 잘 간직하시길.","JPN":"私たちにとっても姉妹にとっても、大事な宝物です。ですから、大事にしてください。","ENG":"It is a precious piece of treasure for us and for you. So please cherish it.","TWN":"無論對我們，還是對修女而言，它都是珍貴的寶物。希望你能好好保管。"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L30_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"BARTENDER_NPC_YOUNG_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"…네! 명심하겠습니다! 신부님!","JPN":"……はい！　肝に銘じます！　神父様！","ENG":"...Okay! You have my word, sir!","TWN":"……是！我會銘記在心的！神父！"},"stage":{"bg":"SKY_SUNSET","bgm":"THEMA_GREMORY","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}}]`);export{e as default};